Third-Party Dependencies
========================

Go Binaries (tools/)
--------------------
The Go tools in this project use only the Go standard library.
No third-party Go modules are imported at runtime.

- Go standard library: BSD-3-Clause license
  https://go.dev/LICENSE

Development Dependencies (not shipped to consumers)
----------------------------------------------------
- TypeScript: Apache-2.0 (https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript)
- Vitest: MIT (https://github.com/vitest-dev/vitest)
- Playwright: Apache-2.0 (https://github.com/microsoft/playwright)
- Rollup: MIT (https://github.com/rollup/rollup)
- Prettier: MIT (https://github.com/prettier/prettier)
- Vite: MIT (https://github.com/vitejs/vite)
- @rollup/plugin-terser: MIT
- rollup-plugin-dts: MIT

Runtime Dependencies
--------------------
None. LiquidJS has zero runtime dependencies.
